Commentary Text: Boult to Shreyas Iyer, out Caught by Samson!! Absolute soft, unlucky dismissal this. A pretty innocuous delivery from Boult -- short and angling down leg. Iyer looks to pull, and there was a clear sound as it went through to the keeper. The umpire's unmoved though. He's even given this a wie. Nah, Samson knows, Iyer knows. RR know. They review. Commentary Text: Kuldeep Sen to Finch, out Bowled!! And he gets a wicket off his first legal delivery. Kuldeep Sen is cock-a-hoop. Finch was sitting on the back foot, trying to negate the inward movement and that meant he couldn't get on top of this 146ks back of a length delivery outside off, goes too hard - trying to slash it through the off-side - and gets a thick inside edge that rattles middle and leg in a jiffy. Finch b Kuldeep Sen 4(7)
